                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="44v"/> The taking of <name type="place">Hurmuz</name> (<date calendar="#Gregorian">1623</date>) by <persName key="person_f1595" role="dpc" change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup">Imām Ḳulī Khān</persName> and his army. (Latin inscription round the fortress).</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="48r"/> The blazing <name type="place">Hurmuz</name> defended by Portuguese.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="49r"/>
                        <persName key="person_f1595" role="dpc" change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup">Imām Ḳulī Khān</persName> in a boat.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="58r"/>
